title: Autumn Glass Pumpkin—Plum
description:
Delicate, graceful hand-blown glass breathes life into a beloved icon of the fall season. A stem falling into curly tendrils adds character to these glistening pumpkins in shades of green, orange, plum and berry. Made exclusively in the USA, and individually signed by the artist, no two are alike. 

4 1/2 x 5 diam.
